  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK822">
<l>iṉampōṉ ṟiṉamallār kēṇmai makaḷir</l>
<l>maṉampōla vēṟu paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The friendship of those who seem to be friends while they are not, will change like the love of women.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
